Definition: any of various deciduous or evergreen ornamental shrubs of the genus Abelia having opposite simple leaves and cymes of small white or pink or purplish flowers
Example: Asia and Mexico
Synonyms: shrub, genus_Abelia, m, any, of, various, deciduous, or, evergreen, ornamental, shrubs, the, genus, Abelia, having, opposite, simple, leaves, and, cymes, small, white, pink, purplish, flowers, Asia, Mexico
Category: noun.plant
